node.title: Three more Omicron cases at New Zealand's border - all unlinked to first case
node.description: The Ministry of Health says it's not surprising, given Omicron's rise globally.
node.content: ["Three further Omicron cases have been detected at New Zealand's border, the Ministry of Health has announced.", "The cases arrived in Auckland from Dubai on December 11 and were transported to a Rotorua MIQ on a bus chartered for international arrivals.", "One case travelled to Dubai from London, the second case travelled to Dubai from Spain and the third travelled to Dubai from Nigeria. All three then boarded the same flight to Auckland.", "The cases are not linked to the first Omicron case reported yesterday.", "More to come."]
